lead_paragraph: Australia coach Michael Cheika will be looking for improvement from the Wallabies next year after losing nine of 15 tests in 2016 but they will have to find it without David Pocock as the standout loose forward embarks on a sabbatical.

headline.print_headline: 'Weirdo' Wallaby Pocock Heading Back to Africa for Year Off
headline.main: 'Weirdo' Wallaby Pocock Heading Back to Africa for Year Off
